rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0001
rows.name: Got any of those Premium Cylinders?

rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently salvaging with one of
those will bag you an incredible
treasure every single time!

rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, strictly speaking it's because they
let you search around in the Cloud Sea for
ages, until you find the best stuff.

rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
The Avaritia Guild can manufacture
ordinary cylinders, but nobody has
the technology to make premium ones.

rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
All the ones you see on the market
were made in ancient times. That's
why they're so rare and expensive.

rows.label: tlk45700111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
If you do have any, I'd
suggest saving them for
when you really need them.
